OL,3,CSeasonal work permit policy to be
OL,4,Creviewed by politicians
OL,6,FJersey politicians have agreed to
OL,7,Fcarry out an independent review of the
OL,8,Fisland's work permit policy.
OL,10,FIn the final States sitting on Monday,
OL,11,FJersey's States Assembly approved the
OL,12,Ffirst part of Deputy Beatriz Poree's
OL,13,Fproposition with 44 votes for, 0
OL,14,Fagainst, and 1 abstention from
OL,15,FConstable Marcus Troy.
OL,17,FThe report will need to be presented
OL,18,Fto the States Assembly by December
OL,19,F2027.
OL,26,@tD@arr
