OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775146264
OL,3,CSeasonal work permit policy to be
OL,4,Creviewed by politicians
OL,6,FA key part of the proposition is to
OL,7,Fallow employees on seasonal work
OL,8,Fpermits in Jersey to hold the work
OL,9,Fpermit licence directly, rather than
OL,10,Fit being tied to their employer.
OL,12,FThis change, if approved, would enable
OL,13,Fseasonal employees to move workplace
OL,14,Fmore easily, which is often tied to
OL,15,Ftheir accommodation, if they face any
OL,16,Fissues.
OL,18,FIt follows the death of Filipino
OL,19,Fseasonal farm worker George Michael
OL,20,FMonte De Ramos Castrudes in January
OL,21,F2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775146264
OL,3,CSeasonal work permit policy to be
OL,4,Creviewed by politicians
OL,6,FHe lived in a property provided by his
OL,7,Femployer, which was described during
OL,8,Fhis inquest as "unfit for human
OL,9,Fhabitation".
OL,11,FThe Coroner concluded Mr Castrudes
OL,12,Fdied from carbon monoxide poisoning
OL,13,Fafter "impulsively" starting a fire to
OL,14,Fkeep warm.
OL,16,FSpeaking in the States previously,
OL,17,FDeputy Poree said: "Migrant workers
OL,18,Fcome to Jersey to try and better their
OL,19,Flives, but that does not mean they
OL,20,Fshould be open to abuse and left
OL,21,Fwithout care and protection.
OL,26,@yD@Krr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
