PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775146264
OL,3,CSeasonal work permit policy to be
OL,4,Creviewed by politicians
OL,6,F"The same care and protection that all
OL,7,Fother workers in the island benefit
OL,8,Ffrom."
OL,10,FLee Madden, CEO of GR8 Recruitment,
OL,11,Fwhich employs around 100 islanders on
OL,12,Fwork permits, told ITV News: "Treat
OL,13,Fpeople right, and they're going to
OL,14,Fstay. As any ethical employer, your
OL,15,Fprimary focus should be on your people
OL,16,Fand making sure that people are
OL,17,Ftreated right."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
