OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1775146264
OL,3,CSeasonal work permit policy to be
OL,4,Creviewed by politicians
OL,6,FHowever, the second part of Deputy
OL,7,FPoree's proposition was rejected,
OL,8,Fwhich relates to reviewing the global
OL,9,FEmployer Pays Principle policy and
OL,10,Fproducing a roadmap of how it might be
OL,11,Fimplemented in Jersey.
OL,13,FPoliticians narrowly refused it with
OL,14,F22 votes for, 22 votes against, and 1
OL,15,Fabstention.
OL,26,@oD@Drr
